title: BATTLE OF FORT WAGNER - North & south II Total War Mod Gameplay
description:
This is my first look at the North & South II mod for Shogun 2 Total War.  In September 7th 1863 the union captured Fort Wagner from confederate control.  But what if the Rebels did a counter attack?  Enjoy the Battle  

Jackie's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/Jackiefishhhhhh

Mod Link: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=649061985&searchtext=north+and+south+

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
